node.text: I'm no activist. There are countless incredible Black voices you should be following to hear this from. All I do is see, hear, and speak as clearly as I can and become a better ally for the Black community. Today would have been Breonna Taylor's 27th birthday. Her case has finally been reopened after a massive wave of petitions and protests. But we cannot stop there. We have to do more in every part of of our daily lives to ensure that police brutality against Black people cannot go unchecked ever again. Donate, march, do whatever you can if you’re able, but most importantly, commit to voicing your support for Black Lives Matter with every breath you take in your school, at your work, and with your family and friends.

node.text: Video dump of a year of love and laughs with this wacky little guy, including when we rescued him! Couldn’t imagine life without him. Pandemic adoptions are being returned to shelters in record numbers - please encourage others to find successful workarounds to keep their pets! #adoptdontshop

node.text: I may be a total homebody, but with #AmazonHalo, I feel much better about it! With its easy-to-use digital tools and a huge library of fitness programs, Halo is helping me build healthier habits, no gym required. 💪 @AmazonHalo #ad

node.text: Happy Mother’s Day, mom. We’ve been through so much hardship and heartbreak over the past year, yet you continue to amaze me with your resilience and radiance. You’re the strongest person I know and I’m so proud to be your son.
